However, the root cause seems to be your index has been corrupted. Removing this and starting over would most likely resolv it, although it may be good if you keep a copy (for future troubleshooting if this needs to be narrowed down), and if you know something weird happened that would have caused the corruption to start with (i.e. machine crashed, power outage, ...)?
